WEBVTT

00:13:29.665 --> 00:13:32.576
because social inequality hurts us all.

00:13:32.600 --> 00:13:36.441
So we need more
compassionate social policies

00:13:36.465 --> 00:13:39.684
that are aimed less at moral education

00:13:39.708 --> 00:13:44.246
and more at promotion
of social justice and equality.

00:13:44.270 --> 00:13:45.469
Thank you.

00:13:45.493 --> 00:13:47.997
(Applause)